{"type":"weapons","title":"Aqua Scepter","summaries":["The <b>Aqua Scepter</b> is a <linked>magic weapon</linked> that can be obtained from <linked>Locked Gold Chests</linked> within the <linked>Dungeon</linked>, or from <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Golden Lock Boxes</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> found in <linked>Dungeon Crates</linked> from <linked>fishing</linked>. It can <linked>auto-fire</linked> an arc of water particles.The projectile can pierce up to 4 targets, hitting a total of 5 targets.<span class=\"eico i1\" title=\"Desktop version\"><b></b><i></i></span> / The projectile can pierce an infinite number of targets.<span class=\"eico i2 i3 i4 i5 i6\" title=\"Console, Old-gen console, Mobile, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>.","The Aqua Scepter can be continuously used to keep enemies juggled. However, the sprite of the Aqua Scepter itself deals no damage. Therefore, an enemy too close to the wielder will not get hit by the water, and simply move past the outstretched wand to hit the player.","Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Mythical</b>."],"statistics":{"Damage":"27 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 16 <span class=\"eico s i6\" title=\"Legacy tModLoader version\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 15 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"small-bold\">(Magic)</span>","Knockback":"7 <span class=\"knockback\">(Strong)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span> <span class=\"eico s i3 i5 i6\" title=\"Old-gen console, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Mana":"7 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i>